VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT CFLAGS\s*=.*\b(-w)\b
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:#pragma\s+warning\s*\(\s*disable|-Wno-error|-w\b|/W0|__attribute__.*unused.*//.*suppress && MISSING:// intentional|// NOLINT
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects flags that suppress compiler warnings.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Suppressing Compiler Warnings.
